data.description: New Roof 11/23. Lovely POOL HOME with 3 bedrooms 2 baths and an office in Ocala's gated Evergreen Estates. Brick pavers and stone accents lead you into the entrance of the home. Glass Side panels and transom window add light to front entry of home. Formal Dining room is separate from the large Living Room and spacious Breakfast Nook. Living room opens to lanai and birdcage through large sliding doors. The public areas of this home have high vaulted ceilings, crown molding, and tile and wood look laminate floors. The Kitchen has granite counter tops and backsplash, breakfast bar, closet pantry, abundant cabinets and new stainless-steel appliances in 2022. The nook overlooks and has access to the Lanai. The Master Bedroom has a tray ceiling, access to the lanai and birdcage, his and her closets and large ensuite bath. This Master Bath has a large soaker garden tub, walk-in shower with rain and handheld heads, separate water closet, split dual vanities, vanity make-up table, and linen closet. This split bedroom home also has 2 carpeted guest bedrooms, a bath with shower tub combo and office/library adjacent to the foyer. The office could be a 4th bedroom if needed. The lanai and birdcage have a ceiling fan, a 13 foot by 13 foot covered area that would make a wonderful outdoor kitchen and dining area and a 24x12 pool for everyone to enjoy. Additional features you’ll enjoy in this home are: ceiling fans with light kits, 2 car garage with storage shelves, interior Laundry room with extra shelving and a slop sink, and privacy fence around the backyard. Be sure to watch our video of this lovely home and make an appointment to see it today. This could be your New Home!
